  <brief_title>A Phase 3 Study to Compare Efficacy and Safety of Masitinib to Placebo in Treatment of Patients With Severe Persistent Asthma Treated With Oral Corticosteroids</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Multicenter, Randomised, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, 2-parallel Groups, Phase 3 Study to Compare the Efficacy and the Safety of Masitinib at 6 mg/kg/Day Versus Placebo in the Treatment of Patients With Severe Persistent Asthma Treated With Oral Corticosteroids</official_title>
