  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study objective is to compare the efficacy and the safety of masitinib at 6 mg/kg/day
      versus placebo in the treatment of patients with Severe Persistent Asthma treated with oral
      corticosteroids.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
